{"tid":1737241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［今晚有銀紙彤追思會］媽媽 ：一定會追究到底","createTime":"2019-11-19T02:02:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T07:35:02.000Z","uid":22556,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"61d88872567636cee4bbc070afeb5dc8924d87a1","tid":1737241,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:02:28.000Z","msg":"網媒《100毛》及《毛記電視》女主播「銀紙彤」曾穎欣 ，本月初在沙田豐盛苑寓所的火警中死亡，涉事單位付之一炬，與銀紙彤同住的父母雖然僥倖脫險，但愛女離世對一家人造成極大打擊。曾媽媽接受《蘋果》獨家訪問中提到，火警當晚她三度將上、下及居住樓層走廊的消防喉拉出欲射水撲火救女，無奈三條消防喉都無水出，結果要待消防員到來才將火警救熄，無法救回女兒一命，成為父母永遠的傷痛，他們更質疑事件或涉及嚴重人為疏忽，「一定會追究到底。」一眾親朋今晚會為穎欣舉行追思會。<br />\n<br />\n豐盛苑單位是任職地盤管工的曾爸爸三十多年前一手購入，他與太太合力建立家園，其後長女及次女穎欣相繼出生，曾媽媽全職湊女，曾爸爸獨自供樓養妻活兒，單位亦已供滿。左鄰右里都是逾三十多年的老街坊，他們對《蘋果》表示，大家都看着曾家女兒從小豆丁長大至亭亭玉立。長女出嫁後已遷出單位，而26歲的銀紙彤是一位孝女，出入都會跟鄰居打招呼，非常有禮貌，街坊鄰里均讚不絕口。對穎欣出事眾人均感可惜，泛淚光。上星期穎欣頭七，鄰居自發買來鮮花及上香，為這年輕早逝的生命作最後悼念，「佢個女真係好乖，我哋都好心痛。」"},{"pid":"4fe453cdb78bdc101c5a83f37409242e6e452756","tid":1737241,"uid":22556,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:03:38.000Z","msg":"「佢係一個天使，犧牲咗自己救我哋。」在父母眼中，穎欣不單孝順，更與胞姊感情要好，從來沒有吵架，曾爸爸哽咽地說，兩個女兒都是他心肝寶貝。「我細個父母要工作，只係畀餐飯我食，帶我去飲餐茶已經好叻，我細個好寂寞，到後來我有兩個女，我會帶佢哋周圍去，唔係我陪佢哋，係佢哋陪我去玩。」<br />\n<br />\n穎欣在浸會大學畢業，心繫媒體工作，畢業後第一份工作就加入了《100毛》，在《毛記電視》之《膠易現場》當女主播，每月獲發工資後，即乖乖給父母6千元家用，今年3月。更為家人安排了一次日本京都之旅，豈料卻是一家人最後一次旅行。曾媽媽翻看舊照，哽咽地說：「我哋三母女着和服，都係欣欣安排㗎......」語畢即俯身大哭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事實上，曾氏一家都彬彬有禮，很受街坊歡迎，慘劇發生後，一班街坊亦特意成立群組照顧曾媽媽，包括輪更煮飯及送愛心湯水。由於曾媽媽情緒非常低落，甚至有街坊自告奮勇在醫院陪夜安撫。事發當晚，曾媽媽由女兒喚醒逃出屋外找消防喉救火，穎欣留在房內，而睡在鄰房的曾爸爸亦被烈火圍困，火警中曾氏夫婦同需送院，兩人都是吸入濃煙不適，其中曾媽媽左手手指燒傷。<br />\n<br />\n曾媽媽留醫九日後出院，最初她經常咳出黑痰及咳嗽，但對女兒的死仍難以釋懷，她特別提到在危急關頭，3個樓層消防喉竟然無水的荒謬事，「3層樓都無水，我當時好無助」。就消防喉無水情況，曾爸爸表示物業管理公司責無旁貸，「作為一個物業管理公司，佢點會容許條消防喉無水？如果你知道無水唔去維修，你就係造假，如果你唔知無水，就係失職！」"},{"pid":"18fd35157bd30eb7d392258aeb6de737cf9d9938","tid":1737241,"uid":22556,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:05:16.000Z","msg":"《蘋果》到豐盛樓視察，火警現場單位仍未解封，走廊及鄰近單位鐵閘及牆身亦被薰黑，「無水」消防喉亦原封不動掛在曾家對出只有數步之遙的牆上。記者在地面升降機大堂發現兩則通告，其中一則內容提到，現時該苑消防設備由「泰星工程服務有限公司」檢查及保養，每年檢查一次，去年12月14日曾完成年檢，並獲消防發出合格證書，管理公司已即時要求承辦商檢查所有消防系統運作正常。<br />\n<br />\n消防處回覆本報查詢會覆，指就有關該大廈的消防設備懷疑損壞事宜，消防處正進行調查。如調查後發現相關人士有違反消防條例的情況，會作出執法行動。<br />\n<br />\n痛失女兒，兩老既要面對喪女之痛；家園盡毀，兩老面臨前路茫茫，他們指目前積蓄難以重建家園，加上火災波及其他單位擔心需作賠償，現時最迫切是找個容身之所。年屆60的曾爸爸，年底前將會退休，原本以為有供滿居屋，加上女兒給予家用，可以退休安享晚年，「我都有個如意算盤，阿女6千蚊，我有少少積蓄，退休應該唔係好大問題，若阿女負擔唔到6千蚊畀我，仲有間居屋，可以逆按揭，我相信我退休生活可以解決。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n世事弄人，悲劇發生，打亂了生活節奏，曾爸爸問過銀行，但回覆稱不會有人願意按揭該單位，地產經紀亦稱無論出租還是出售，均一個字﹕難！「等唔介意租我層樓的人出現，等唔介意買一個兇宅，而又無按揭，又有經濟能力，一次過畀一嚿錢出來的人，以佢哋經驗，可能要三幾年先會出現，咁我呢三幾年都好麻煩。」<br />\n<br />\n面臨經濟危機，曾爸爸雖有購買家居保險，但保險公司說暫時會凍結保險金，以先應付他人賠償，「保險公司稱即使有賠償，會暫時凍結先應付其他有可能嘅賠償，有剩先會畀返我哋，而且唔係一筆過，係實報實銷，即只可以幫我做一個有限基本維修，至於傢俬電器等等到時睇情況。」<br />\n<br />\n現時兩老暫住大女住所，日前有人介紹他們租住土瓜灣一個明年清拆的唐樓單位，但曾媽媽指唐樓雖平租但擔心防火設備欠佳，經歷今次火災已經怕怕，若最後真的找不到合適單位亦要租住，她指現時有向社署求助「希望可以恩恤安置一個臨時居所畀我哋渡過難關，以後日子，再咬緊牙關慢慢行落去。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191119&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60277559\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191119%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60277559&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfGhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=b4b8a222\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191119%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60277559&h=811b044e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191119&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60277559</a>"},{"pid":"ca23ee03841a9926e5f8117b395460a6309a9a9e","tid":1737241,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:29:33.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b55ba698f7f5de113b139e041b77df3248fddd8","tid":1737241,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:30:13.000Z","msg":"唉 安息"},{"pid":"f55c9ae4a12d2669c5bb6283c1c5a0bd962e4da0","tid":1737241,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f067425ff88754f06df0689123b249c84fd9c45","tid":1737241,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:32:40.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"b27637e0255012b4334fe8c92724ecb2514b4f66","tid":1737241,"uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:37:15.000Z","msg":"不過我搵左好耐都無追思會 時間同地點😞"},{"pid":"b044334d17cabb5ffbf07f3239255ca44556c5dc","tid":1737241,"uid":3241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:42:47.000Z","msg":"咩撚野家居保險黎，佢用邊間公證行<br />\n大佬呀，家居保險分財產部份同第三者責任保險<br />\n財產部份分別由50萬至過百萬保額不等，你燒到咁一定有得賠嫁喎，係咪而家保險公司玩野要等消防處出報告，以我去睇似係保險公司覺得有著火原因有可疑，覺得係戶主家人有不法行為令到起火先會拖CLAIM<br />\n第三者果PART保額通常係5百萬至1千萬，基本上僅僅夠賠樓上下左右既損失。<br />\n所以話家居保一定一定要買，但係要搵間唔好咁賤格既公司"},{"pid":"e8ac10abbd273ff58b285b692442840af3adcb86","tid":1737241,"uid":281972,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:43:02.000Z","msg":"安息喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c2ecb35eca6257bf186875e47f3b5476b49584","tid":1737241,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:46:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb8403fadbc5c07766391b14fac73f2adcbfea11","tid":1737241,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:49:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5288aba7518bb5e43d93b630e8a4b67526ff65c4","tid":1737241,"uid":48176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:50:15.000Z","msg":"睇完喊左....安息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7470ffd464cd0c92be2819a76f6e34771f64a1af","tid":1737241,"uid":332448,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:50:41.000Z","msg":"手足，Rip"},{"pid":"e4e13dc9101724c0858842947ba347cf4dfd2a54","tid":1737241,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:52:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca119a9a7c9d21939b798d80b89f6ccbc2ec2398","tid":1737241,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:53:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f34b97308286a5e033656d2ce998110588bfbea","tid":1737241,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:56:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d9714a8608cbeaaafeccb84a0cc17a47a040ab3","tid":1737241,"uid":6562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:59:12.000Z","msg":"好慘..."},{"pid":"2239a6cf86cb265e36f5c73b322d51f060ba982d","tid":1737241,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:01:05.000Z","msg":"冇水？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f4a44b0ea88b66bcddc9243beeeb142af2e418","tid":1737241,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:21:34.000Z","msg":"無時間地點"},{"pid":"708f815941e5e9f5d4c69467bf9e1225f289be17","tid":1737241,"uid":78764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:22:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"879b84564571dc8251893cb629699e76a1f202f0","tid":1737241,"uid":297603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:23:59.000Z","msg":"曾穎欣校友之告別禮:<br />\n謹定於大圍寶福紀念館設靈，<br />\n11月19日星期二 告別禮<br />\n親友19：00後可到寶福紀念館2樓2C寶德堂， 告別禮19：30開始，預計一小時<br />\n交通請見以下網址<br />\n<a href=\"https://funeral.pofookhill.com/%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffuneral.pofookhill.com%2F%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2580%259A%2F&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfGhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=ed44d1e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://funeral.pofookhill.com/%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A/</a><br />\n<br />\n11月20日星期三出殯 <br />\n上午10:00舉行出殯禮上午10:30隨即出殯<br />\n<br />\n願曾穎欣校友主懷安息。主祐大家平安！"},{"pid":"6d90099f5f7fb44efdd50b8b841f136530f4dbdf","tid":1737241,"uid":36049,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:25:15.000Z","msg":"屌你老味點解好人要咁死<br />\n班仆街死黑警可以咁安全"},{"pid":"7a3dba0bcd7305347e5af0f64881459bcb0b4f31","tid":1737241,"uid":46033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:29:46.000Z","msg":"呢D先父母失去仔女既正常反應, <br />\n<br />\n之前果D父母反應..........."},{"pid":"d26962b417698b223a01c2a44fc1a3c24b9a87cb","tid":1737241,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a3dba0bcd7305347e5af0f64881459bcb0b4f31","tid":1737241,"uid":46033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:29:46.000Z","msg":"呢D先父母失去仔女既正常反應, <br />\n<br />\n之前果D父母反應..........."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:34:53.000Z","msg":"係文字上都睇到個反應，真係勁"}]}